    <item>
      <title>ASML股票下跌，首席执行官说地缘政治风险构成挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/asml-ceo-says-global-tensions-harm-innovation-as-us-tariffs-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对来自欧洲联盟的产品征收20％关税之后，ASML Holding NV的股票是半导体制造中最先进的机器的唯一生产商，在一年多以来，这有可能破坏公司的供应链。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/asml-ceo-says-global-tensions-harm-innovation-as-us-tariffs-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 10:46:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Microsoft撤回了从芝加哥到雅加达的数据中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/microsoft-pulls-back-on-data-centers-from-chicago-to-jakarta</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Microsoft Corp.已将全球数据中心项目撤回，这表明该公司正在仔细研究其计划，以构建为人工智能和云提供动力的服务器农场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/microsoft-pulls-back-on-data-centers-from-chicago-to-jakarta</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 09:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果生产中心受到关税的打击，使股票暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/apple-shares-slide-after-tariffs-threaten-to-hit-production-hubs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司（Apple Inc.）在总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的新关税中直接发现自己，即使经过一年的努力使iPhone制造商免受贸易战和供应链中断的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/apple-shares-slide-after-tariffs-threaten-to-hit-production-hubs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
